y: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"> - 창술서(인크리즈 레인지)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"> - 창술서(인크리즈 레인지)(소생)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 102, 0); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">* 클래스 가호</span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 102, 0); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 클래스별 랭킹 1위에게 지급되는 \'클래스 가호\'가 2~3위에게도 지급되도록 변경되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"> 1) 순위 별 지급</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">  - 1~3위까지 클래스 가호 아이템 지급</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"> 2) 효과</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">  (1) 1위</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">   - HP +300, PVP 대미지 감소 +10</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">  (2) 2위</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">   - HP +150, PVP 대미지 감소 +5</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">  (2) 3위</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">   - HP +100, PVP 대미지 감소 +3</div><br></div>', 17, 1, 'false', NULL),
(38, 'GameMaster', '2021-07-22 18:42:38', '7/22 Update Notes', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\">* 버림받은 자들의 땅(인터) 수정사항</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 버림받은 자들의 땅(인터) 사냥터에 섬 지역이(Safety Zone) 추가되었습니다</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">2. 버림받은 자들의 땅(인터) 입장위치가 섬으로 변경 되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">3. 랜덤 텔레포트’를 통해 사냥터로 이동 가능합니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">4. 사냥터에서 귀환 시 섬 지역으로 이동됩니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">5. 섬 지역에서 NPC를 통해 로컬 서버로 이동 가능합니다.</div>', 38, 1, 'false', NULL),
