(40, 'GameMaster', '2021-09-13 15:44:29', '8/25 Mirror War', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\">* 거울전쟁</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\">1. \'이계의 존재\'가 기란 감옥 2층을 침공합니다.<br style=\"outline: initial;\">&nbsp;1) 침공시간: 12시 ~ 24시 사이랜덤 출현 (단, 확률 출현으로 매일 출현하지 않을 수 있음)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\">&nbsp;2) 출현장소: 기란감옥 2층</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></d