(51, 'GameMaster', '2022-01-28 01:02:26', '9/23 Update Notice', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\">1. \'쿠거의 가더\' 착용 클래스에 전사가 추가 되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\">2. +10 용의 티셔츠(지룡/화룡/풍룡/수룡) 아이템의 최대 HP 증가 옵션이 아래와 같이 변경됩니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\">- 기존: HP +100</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.7px;\"=\"\">- 변경: HP +200</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system,