(59, 'GameMaster', '2022-01-28 01:12:37', '12/22 Forgotten Island', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\">* 잊혀진 섬(로컬)</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 잊혀진 섬(로컬 서버)이 추가되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;1) 오픈 시간</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- 매주 토/일 09:00 ~ 18:00</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, san