(63, 'GameMaster', '2022-02-24 12:27:47', '2/23 Mirrior War Season 2', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\">* 거울 전쟁 시즌2</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 이벤트 기간 동안 \'이계의 존재\'가 기란 감옥 2층을 침공합니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;1) 침공시간: 18시 ~ 22시 사이랜덤 출현(확률 출현)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;2) 출현장소: 기란감옥 2층</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: HelveticaNeue-Light, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; outline: initial;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0);\">* 그 외</span></span></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">1. 공성 선포 혈맹 군주에 대한 선포 마크 표시가 수호탑 주위로 변경되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">2. 켄트성 성주 왕관 이미지가 변경되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">3. 성주 왕관 표시가 상시 표시에서 마우스 오버 시 표시로 변경되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">4. 파티 심플 UI 모드가 추가되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;1) 파티 심플 UI 표시 정보</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp; - 클래스, 캐릭터명, HP</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">5. 아이템 삭제 알림 표시가 추가되었습니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;1) 삭제일정 미도래: ICON에 연두색 꺽쇠 표시</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;2) 삭제일정 경과: ICON 음영처리</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">&nbsp;3) 삭제일정 24시간이내 도래: ICON 모래시계 표시</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">리니지와 함께 즐거운 시간 보내시기 바랍니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: -0.7px;\">고맙습니다.</div></div>', 14, 1, 'false', NULL),
