(70, 'GameMaster', '2022-09-29 00:31:32', '9/28 Update Notice', '<p><span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" outline:=\"\" initial;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgba(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0.93);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* 제련 시스템</span></span><br style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" outline:=\"\" initial;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgba(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0.93);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;\"=\"\"><br style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" outline:=\"\" initial;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgba(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0.93);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;\"=\"\">1. 제련 시스템이 추가 되었습니다.</span><br style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" outline:=\"\" initial;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgba(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0.93);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;\"=\"\"><br style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" outline:=\"\" initial;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgba(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0.93);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 18px;\"=\"\"><span style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial