(81, 'GameMaster', '2023-02-08 23:35:48', '2/8 Update Notice', '<div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700; outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"outline: initial; color: rgb(204, 102, 0); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* 군주 리부트</span></span><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. 군주의 아래 스킬이 리뉴얼 되었습니다.<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;1) 샤이닝 아머<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) 기존<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- ER +10<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (2) 변경<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;- ER/DG +5, 90레벨부터 2레벨당 +1(최대 +10)</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;2) 프라임<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) 변경 사항<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; - 시전자 본인에게는 지역 무관 siege zone 효과 적용</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;3) 엠파이어<br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; (1) 변경 사항<br style=\"outline: initial; l