); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">리니지와 함께 즐거운 시간 보내시기 바랍니다.</div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\"><br style=\"outline: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div data-contents-type=\"text\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; outline: initial; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.93); font-size: 18px;\">고맙습니다.</div>', 4, 1, 'false', NULL);
